These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: orchid, begonia
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, bus
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, pakistani
2 different games are played: billiard, bridge
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, pall-mall
1. the pakistani is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the trike is in an even position##4
4. the pall-mall-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Flower   | orchid     | begonia     |
| Transport   | bus     | trike |
| Nationality   | nigerian | pakistani  |
| Game           | bridge    | billiard |
| Cigar         | pall-mall   | blend       |

