.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda
House: gothic-revival, modern
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, malaysian
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, zinnia
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, jet-ski
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
2. the indonesian is the gothic-revival house##1
3. the indonesian is in an even position##4
4. the modern house is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | almond-milk |
| House           | modern  | gothic-revival     |
| Nationality   | malaysian       | indonesian      |
| Flower           | balloon-flower        | zinnia      |
| Transport         | jet-ski | car     |

