House: palace, wooden
2 different games are played: canasta, chess
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, skateboard
1. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is in an odd position##4
4. the wooden house is the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Flower         | daffodil     | zinnia    |
| House           | palace     | wooden |
| Game   | chess    | canasta   |
| Beverage         | 7up | hot-chocolate   |
| Transport     | helicopter | skateboard |

