.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-4::.
There 2 different types of food: cranberry, kiwi
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, motorbike
City: nizza, berlin
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, may
2 different games are played: monopoly, bridge
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |
| Food          | kiwi     | cranberry     |
| Transport   | boat   | motorbike        |
| City   | berlin      | nizza         |
| Birthday   | may | october       |
| Game         | monopoly  | bridge |

