There are 2 different nationalities: polish, japanese
2 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, rock
There are 2 different favourite colors: red, mauve
1. the fan of rock is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
2. the person playing monopoly is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Sport      | badminton     | parkour     |
| Nationality          | polish | japanese |
| Game   | scrabble  | monopoly  |
| Music-Genre   | disco    | rock       |
| Color     | mauve      | red     |

