2. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
4. the fan of soul is the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
