2. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person who growsorchid is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is climbing is the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3

