1. the person eating banana is the fan of country##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
3. the modern house is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of country is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| House      | modern      | cottage     |
| Music-Genre   | metal    | country  |
| Game           | poker   | billiard |
| Food         | radish | banana |
| Cigar     | swisher     | cain     |

 